messages.text: The phone you’re holding contains one other number. This is your companion. You’ll need her help to escape- but can you trust her?
You may begin now. Good luck.
I only remember going to sleep in my bed
Is there anything you can see around you?
The ceiling is so low I can only crawl
I’m shouting, can you hear me?
I don’t think so. Try going around the room.
I’m using this phone as a flashlight
I crawled straight to the far side of the room.
I have a door here too, also locked
What if we can’t get out??
Reread the text we got. it’s a game
I see five number keys. Right now they’re at 9-7-2-6-2
Do you think our combos would be the same?
My first three numbers are gold, the last two are silver
Your last two numbers are gold?
Alright we can both try the combo 9-7-2-3-1
It worked! Did it work for you?
Now I’m in a corridor. I’m guessing you are too
This building or whatever we’re in seems symmetrical
Let’s figure out a way to get to the center, this will be easier if we can meet up
There are two turns I can go down
I’m June. Did you ever do a corn maze when you were younger
Every autumn. You want me to keep my right hand on the wall until I make it through, right?
I always used my left hand, but yes
Text you on the other side :)
Alright. Is there another locked door in front of you?
Really? I don’t have one. What does it say
“You and your companion’s electronic locks are synchronized.
Enter on the pad your companion’s computer password and both of your doors will unlock.”
This one’s really easy! What is it?
This is very strange. I used it yesterday but I’ve forgotten the password
They must have done something to you.
My head hurts trying to think about it
Okay… Just start from scratch. What would you put as a password right now?
I have to sit down for a little
Just my mother. My father wasn’t there
She supported us my whole life but now she can’t pay the medical bills
I think she’s dying but she won’t admit it
I’m starting to feel a little better
Take deep breaths. You did a really good job.
We wouldn’t have gotten anywhere without you. :)
I’m walking- what do you see?
Me too. It’s daytime. Let’s walk toward it
Oh no. Do you see what I see?
There’s a giant pit between where I’m standing and the exit
Also… a desk? It has two levers
These are an extremely rare cut
I’m almost positive they’re worth millions
Don’t make any decisions before we discuss it, okay?
“Keep the diamonds in the drawer or no lever will move. Pull either the left or right lever.
If you and your companion both pull the right levers, the diamonds will be incinerated and a bridge will appear for the both of you.
“If one of you pulls the left and the other the right, The left-puller will have a bridge appear and will be able to keep the diamonds.
The right-puller’s platform will fall out beneath her.
“If both of you pull the left lever, both platforms will fall.”
...Thank you for repeating it to me honestly
You had the opportunity to trick me
June, let’s just talk it through.
We both just want to get OUT of here, right?
We made it this far, we just want to survive!
Okay, good. I’ll be your friend for LIFE if we both just pull the right lever. Let’s just both pull the right one and get out okay?
It means everything to me that we got through this together. I don’t have many friends...
...but you helped me in the scariest situation I’ve ever been in
But I’m sorry, I need to save my mother. I need the money to save her life
She’s the only person I have
